'''埃尔科'''（{{lang en|'''Elko'''}}）<ref>Beverly Crum & Jon P. Dayley, ''Shoshoni Texts'' (1997, Boise State University), pg. 167</ref>位于[[美国|美国]][[内华达州|内华达州]]东北部，是[[埃尔科县_(内华达州)|埃尔科县]]的县治。{{GR|6}}<ref name="Profile for Elko, Nevada, NV">{{cite web|url= http://www.epodunk.com/cgi-bin/genInfo.php?locIndex=17670|title= Profile for Elko, Nevada, NV|publisher= ePodunk|accessdate= September 26, 2012|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170420124429/http://www.epodunk.com/cgi-bin/genInfo.php?locIndex=17670|archive-date= 2017-04-20|dead-url= yes}}</ref>整個埃尔科都會區還要比[[埃爾科縣|埃爾科縣]]大。<ref>[http://www.census.gov/population/www/estimates/metro_general/2006/List5.txt MICROPOLITAN STATISTICAL AREAS AND COMPONENTS] {{Wayback|url=http://www.census.gov/population/www/estimates/metro_general/2006/List5.txt |date=20070629011245 }}, [[Office_of_Management_and_Budget|Office of Management and Budget]], 2007-05-11.  Accessed 2008-07-27.</ref>

根据[[2000年美国人口普查|2000年美国人口普查]]，共有20,732人，其中[[白人|白人]]占81.5%、[[土著美国人|土著美国人]]占5.4%、[[亚裔美国人|亚裔美国人]]占1.0%。{{GR|2}}這個數字於2010年下降18,297人。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/ |title=2010 census factfinder2 |accessdate=2013-07-29 |archive-date=2013-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130911234518/http://factfinder2.census.gov/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

